        <h3 class="forma-following__empty-title">
          Follow brands you love.
        </h3>

        <p class="forma-following__empty-text">
          Keep track of new arrivals, stories and inspiration from your
          favourite brands.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/pages/brands"
          class="forma-following__empty-link"
